Get experiment Accessids and name use get_compendia to check all the available compendia

get_experiments.Rd

Get experiment Accessids and name use get_compendia to check all the available compendia

get_experiments(compendium = "vitis_vinifera", sampleName = NULL)

Arguments

compendium

a character - the selected compendium
sampleName

a character - if NULL(default) returns all available experiments ids for the selected compendium

Value

a data.frame with experimentAccessId and EsperimentName

Examples

get_experiments(sampleName="GSM671721")
